    @Named
 @Singleton
public class URLLicenseInfoParser
extends ConcurrentSkipListMap<String,AnyLicenseInfo>
implements DefaultMethods
    URL (String representation) to AnyLicenseInfo Map implementation. The ConcurrentSkipListMap.get(Object) method transparently calculates and caches any value.
